## Recommended Execution Order

```
Week 1: Sprint 1 (Fixes 1–8)  →  All rework loops functional
Week 2: Sprint 2 (Fixes 9–14) →  Schema gaps closed, auto-triggers working
Week 3: Sprint 3 (Fixes 15–23) →  UI reflects live data, no hardcoded sections
Week 4: Sprint 4 (Fixes 24–29) →  Polish and production readiness
```

After Sprint 1 alone, the app will go from **65% → ~85%** PRD compliance.  
After all 4 sprints, the app reaches **~97%** PRD compliance (remaining 3% = external calendar/PDM integrations, which are out of scope per the PRD itself).
